abstract: Texas Rangers second baseman Jurickson Profar is expected to miss second consecutive season following shoulder surgery.
lead_paragraph: Texas Rangers second baseman Jurickson Profar, once the team’s top prospect, had shoulder surgery and was expected to miss his second straight season.

headline.main: Rangers’ Profar Will Miss a Second Season
headline.print_headline: Rangers’ Profar to Miss a 2nd Season
